      <item>
        <title>Vagrant Environment for Symfony Projects</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://miriamtocino.github.io/images/symfony-love-vagrant.svg&quot; alt=&quot;Symfony Love Vagrant&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When I first started to work with Symfony, it was important for me to create a smooth and quick way to set up a development environment every time I would like to start a new project.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kleiram&quot;&gt;Ramon Kleiss&lt;/a&gt; already built a box, which turned out to fit all my needs at first. It provides a virtual environment for Symfony2 development using &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vagrantup.com/&quot;&gt;Vagrant&lt;/a&gt;. You can download it and read its full documentation &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/kleiram/vagrant-symfony&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But there was still something missing. How could I use this type of virtual box in different Symfony projects at the same time without having to use the built-in Symfony web server?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;I wanted to be able to check two different projects in my browser running locally, without getting too much into trouble.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;step-by-step-guide&quot;&gt;Step-by-Step Guide&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Download the Vagrant virtual box from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/kleiram/vagrant-symfony&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; and save it under your documents (I save all important downloaded files under a common folder &lt;strong&gt;downloads&lt;/strong&gt; under my &lt;strong&gt;Projects&lt;/strong&gt; folder).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add the &lt;strong&gt;vagrant-symfony-master&lt;/strong&gt; folder that you just downloaded to your project root folder and rename it into &lt;strong&gt;vagrant&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Open the &lt;strong&gt;Vagrantfile&lt;/strong&gt; and configure the network interfaces by changing the IP address (replace &lt;strong&gt;192.168.56.101&lt;/strong&gt; in the following example) and the ports (replace &lt;strong&gt;1234&lt;/strong&gt; in the following example).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;It is important to remark that you must use different ports for the different projects, otherwise you wonâ€™t be able to run various projects at the same time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The rest of the file you could leave as it is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# wonderful-project/vagrant/Vagrantfile&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Vagrant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;configure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;2&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Configure the box to use&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;box&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;precise64&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;box_url&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;http://files.vagrantup.com/precise64.box&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Configure the network interfaces&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;network&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:private_network&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;ip&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;192.168.56.101&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;network&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:forwarded_port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;guest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;80&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1234&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;network&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:forwarded_port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;guest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;8081&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1234&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;network&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:forwarded_port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;guest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;3306&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1234&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;network&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:forwarded_port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;guest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;27017&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1234&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Configure shared folders&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;synced_folder&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;/vagrant&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;vagrant-root&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:nfs&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;17&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;synced_folder&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;..&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;/var/www&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;application&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:nfs&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kp&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Configure VirtualBox environment&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;provider&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:virtualbox&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;wonderful-project&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;customize&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;modifyvm&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;--memory&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;512&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;23&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;24&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Provision the box&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;vm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;provision&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:ansible&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ansible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;27&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ansible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;playbook&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;ansible/site.yml&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;28&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;29&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Go to your &lt;strong&gt;hosts&lt;/strong&gt; file under the folder &lt;strong&gt;~/etc&lt;/strong&gt; and add your project to the list:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# ~/etc/hosts&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# ...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; 192.168.56.101     wonderful-project.dev&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can now go back to your project folder in the terminal and build up your new virtual box. It could take a while the first time you run this, so it could be a good moment to grab a coffee or tea ;-):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /wonderful-project/vagrant
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;vagrant up&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can now see that the new VM has been added into &lt;strong&gt;Virtual Box&lt;/strong&gt;. In the terminal you can access it connecting via ssh. The project will be located under &lt;strong&gt;/var/www&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /wonderful-project/vagrant
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;vagrant ssh
&lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# ssh connection successful&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /var/www&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You may also want to configure the connection to the database in a program such as &lt;strong&gt;SequelPro&lt;/strong&gt;. The settings would look something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt;: wonderful-project&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Host&lt;/strong&gt;: 192.168.56.101&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Username&lt;/strong&gt;: root&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Password&lt;/strong&gt;: null&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Database&lt;/strong&gt;: wonderful-project&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Port&lt;/strong&gt;: 3306 (default)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You may also want to configure the connection to the virtual machine via SFTP in a program such as &lt;strong&gt;Transmit&lt;/strong&gt;. The settings would look something like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt;: wonderful-project&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Host&lt;/strong&gt;: 192.168.56.101&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Username&lt;/strong&gt;: vagrant&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Password&lt;/strong&gt;: vagrant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You are now ready to go back to your project and configure the &lt;strong&gt;parameters.yml&lt;/strong&gt; file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# wonderful-project/app/config/parameters.yml&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt; parameters:
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;   database_driver: pdo_mysql
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;   database_host: 192.168.56.101
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;   database_port: null
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt;   database_name: wonderful-project
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;   database_user: root
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;   database_password: null
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;   mailer_transport: smtp
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;   mailer_host: 192.168.56.101
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;   mailer_user: null
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;   mailer_password: null
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;   locale: en
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;   secret: ThisTokenIsNotSoSecretChangeIt&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;on-a-daily-basis&quot;&gt;On a daily basis&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I like to save all the different projects that I am working on in a table like this under my documents, specially to keep track of the ports that I am already using:&lt;/p&gt;

